          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "5073a6f3",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "Join us\n<h2>In our mission to keep commercial floors pristine and our customers delighted.</h2>\nMidland Floors is not just a workplace\u2014it's a place where craftsmanship meets quality and where your contributions will directly impact our esteemed clientele\u2019s satisfaction. Take the opportunity to elevate your career to the next level by joining our esteemed team. Fill out your application today and let's make Washington D.C.'s floors shine together.\n\nIf you have the skills, passion, and commitment to excellence that define the Midland Floors ethos, we encourage you to apply. Completing our employment application is the first step towards a rewarding career with a company that values hard work, dedication, and a keen eye for detail.\n\n\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/7-essential-tips-for-impeccable-commercial-floor-care-services/\">7 Essential Tips for Impeccable Commercial Floor Care Services</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/eco-friendly-floor-solutions-for-retail-stores/\">Eco-Friendly Floor Solutions for Retail Stores</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a>\n\n<a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/the-latest-in-commercial-floor-tech-innovations-for-2024/\">The Latest in Commercial Floor Tech: Innovations for 2024</a>",
                "align": "left",
                "text_color": "#0F1411",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_size": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 17,
                  "sizes": []
                },
                "typography_line_height": {
                  "unit": "em",
                  "size": 1.7,
                  "sizes": []
                }
              },
              "elements": [],
              "isInner": false
            }
          ],
